{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they were notified, but I wasn't notified.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And when I came, then the conductor said that there is-- he wanted me to meet someone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that was Stephan Deak, who was a Hungarian violinist, unemployed without working permission, and in a pretty bad state-- very, very poor, and in a very bad state.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And somehow-- I don't know-- I mean, he didn't-- until then, from the time that I had this-- that I was put into prison with the-- from the one man I ever slept with, I never accepted from any man a cup of coffee or anything.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I didn't go out with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I-- people invited me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I never, never accepted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I absolutely refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But he was so-- first of all, he knew quite a lot of my friends from Budapest, from the whole circle that I knew and I moved in in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Then he, he-- he didn't want to go to bed with me straight away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And, and somehow, we started going out together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he was in that terrible state, but I always thought that because he was hungry and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And eventually, we decided that one, one room is cheaper than two rooms, and that we are going to get married.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We didn't have-- I mean, I should have run.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "When I went to his studio, I should have run.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Because all the papers were on the f-- I mean, the way it looked, it was so filthy and everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I should have run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But I didn't run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I felt sorry for him, because he was in even worse state.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And he lost his parents and everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And so I, I didn't run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And we eventually got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I mean, it's too long to tell how.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
